*She lets out another blood curdling scream.  Her shoulder was about to fall 
off her small body.  She crawled to a tree and rested at the base of it.  
Her body drained of most of it's mech fluid and her wounds becoming worse.  
Her open side was very slowly tring to repair itself but with little 
success.  She was beathing heavily. Sweat was starting to drip down her face 
plates. She had so little strength left.  She could hardly move after that 
last blast from Transanulas. She tried to move but couldn't.  All she could 
do was lay there and hope the Matrix would show her mercy.*
